{"tid":1487740,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[8.31新口號] 忘初衷，雨。時並進，光復香港，時代革命","createTime":"2019-08-19T11:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T11:42:31.000Z","uid":1858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4945af196eab9a71d00a993a728b1aa9745fb5e2","tid":1487740,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:35:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毋忘初衷，雨。時並進，光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n      相信大家都認同8.31係一個十分十分十分之重要嘅日子，雨傘革命嘅五周年。<br />\n<br />\n     曾經，好多人都定義雨傘革命係失敗左，包括我。但係自從6.9打到依家，大家無論係勇武應變，和理非文宣都同雨革個時係兩個層次，呢兩場革命嘅最終目的一樣係推翻獨裁政府，尋獲與我們既生嘅自由，所以，我懇請大家承認雨革係時代革命嘅上集。<br />\n<br />\n     上集我地之所以未能成功爭取係因為當時仍然有好多香港人未訓醒，依家經歷左呢五年嘅洗禮，係遊行入面我可以感覺到大師兄已經翻黎喇，至於未醒個d個人認為佢地只會繼續昏迷不醒，希望大家可以將上一集嘅教誨延續落時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n     小弟不才，只係將上集嘅精華`毋忘初衷&lsquo;加入現有口號，希望香港人可以真正做到不失焦，不分化，不篤灰，不流血，不受傷，不被捕，不割席。<br />\n至於雨。時並進，相信明眼人一睇就知係雨革同時革一同前進，除左係紀念雨革之外，亦係想有合拼／延續嘅意思。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毋忘初衷，雨。時並進，光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc4fd6639a9a971224c086c2a2f91a150aa73908","tid":1487740,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:35:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">823</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7fESbQo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fESbQo.jpg&h=c5df1785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">824</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OKWk5aO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOKWk5aO.jpg&h=16be77f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0rAT38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0rAT38.jpg&h=3b5dc8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">825</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZSDRRz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZSDRRz.jpg&h=aa1267e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1da8ea8d45bbec62002579f860d51bf766102c03","tid":1487740,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fa9c03d798168cae403497a61bba7ae92d16f3","tid":1487740,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:36:09.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"55924e2a0da42e7e107a5e7346bd54be81c6870b","tid":1487740,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"609aec658e9e89856150d8497bd9ae67ac9eb8ac","tid":1487740,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:37:25.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"0ed081cb21af7dcd091c727b71268fcdea436583","tid":1487740,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:38:42.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"b6949efdccc701e7feff83aa44a6512e6c492243","tid":1487740,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:39:27.000Z","msg":"831<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef790e88c844a35f181dc11aa3a98e86225ceb7","tid":1487740,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:42:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">毋忘初衷，雨。時並進，光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"}]}